Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.72,0:01:08.10,tiagop,,0,0,0,,Strive to create warmth and sunshine
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.10,0:01:10.02,tiagop,,0,0,0,,For my little sister’s wish
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.14,0:01:13.14,tiagop,,0,0,0,,Nothing matters even if I’m hurt
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.31,0:01:15.97,tiagop,,0,0,0,,We fight alien forces together
