Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.33,0:01:43.00,Default,,0,0,0,,It’s so warm out.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.50,0:01:48.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I’m so thirsty. I need a drink!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.50,0:01:52.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I’ll get you some, Mr. Slowy!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.75,0:01:54.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Here, Mr. Slowy.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.41,0:01:56.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Your drink.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.41,0:02:01.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Rest for a bit, Mr. Slowy.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.00,0:02:04.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Weslie.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.66,0:02:07.00,Default,,0,0,0,,It’s nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.75,0:02:10.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Weslie’s incredible.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.58,0:02:15.66,Default,,0,0,0,,There, there, I’ll help you—
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.50,0:02:19.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Here’s your kite.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.50,0:02:30.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.91,0:02:33.00,Default,,0,0,0,,What a huge log!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.08,0:02:33.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Leave it to—
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.58,0:02:43.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Weslie!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.75,0:02:47.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.41,0:02:52.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.66,0:02:54.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Weslie is able to help so many people.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.08,0:02:57.50,Default,,0,0,0,,If only I had gadgets, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.33,0:02:59.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Gadgets?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.41,0:03:06.00,Default,,0,0,0,,All done!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.16,0:03:09.91,Default,,0,0,0,,There’s no way Wolffy will find out
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.91,0:03:12.50,Default,,0,0,0,,that I’m living above his ceiling.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.66,0:03:14.33,Default,,0,0,0,,With such a clean environment,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.58,0:03:17.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I’ll surely come up with a way to capture BB Goat.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.00,0:03:27.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.91,0:03:30.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me see what Wolffy is up to.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.00,0:03:34.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Why is this refrigerator so complicated?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.33,0:03:37.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I’m an inventor, yet even I can’t get it fixed.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.25,0:03:39.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Why call yourself an “inventor”
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.91,0:03:42.08,Default,,0,0,0,,when you can’t even fix a refrigerator?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.25,0:03:44.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Let’s try using this!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.75,0:03:50.58,Default,,0,0,0,,How clumsy. I’ll have to take matters into my own hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.83,0:04:07.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Fixing a refrigerator isn’t {\i1}that{\i0} complicated.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.33,0:04:10.08,Default,,0,0,0,,This will do.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.75,0:04:13.58,Default,,0,0,0,,All done.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.08,0:04:17.00,Default,,0,0,0,,The refrigeration capacity of this thing is awful, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.58,0:04:19.41,Default,,0,0,0,,It couldn’t even keep my ice cream cold last time.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.66,0:04:20.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.58,0:04:23.41,Default,,0,0,0,,All done!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.58,0:04:26.50,Default,,0,0,0,,But the chocolate I stored last time only lasted me two days.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.91,0:04:28.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I’ll increase its volume, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.33,0:04:32.08,Default,,0,0,0,,There we go!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.33,0:04:35.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me test it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.91,0:04:38.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I may have overdone it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.83,0:04:39.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.41,0:04:42.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I could this to capture BB Goat.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.00,0:04:53.91,Default,,0,0,0,,No one’s here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.08,0:04:55.91,Default,,0,0,0,,If I get the Super Cube,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.25,0:04:59.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I might just get to Weslie’s level!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.33,0:05:02.91,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.91,0:05:04.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Slowy?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.66,0:05:06.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no, have I been caught?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.75,0:05:09.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.91,0:05:10.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.58,0:05:12.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I was worried that the Super Cube might get stolen,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.66,0:05:14.08,Default,,0,0,0,,so I came to check on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.75,0:05:19.41,Default,,0,0,0,,With this top-tier security system that I invented,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.58,0:05:22.41,Default,,0,0,0,,no one will dare to take the Cube under my watch!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.50,0:05:27.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I nearly set it off.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.75,0:05:30.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I need to go out for some materials now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.58,0:05:44.41,Default,,0,0,0,,It’s been stolen!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.75,0:05:46.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Slowy,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.25,0:05:47.58,Default,,0,0,0,,the Super Cube—
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.58,0:05:50.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop worrying about the Cube, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.66,0:05:52.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Let’s go, Sparky.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.33,0:05:59.83,Default,,0,0,0,,BB Goat, this Cube is very important.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.91,0:06:00.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Don’t mess around with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.50,0:06:05.25,Default,,0,0,0,,What if I “accidentally” get a gadget
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.25,0:06:07.08,Default,,0,0,0,,when returning the Super Cube to Mr. Slowy?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.08,0:06:08.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.33,0:06:09.91,Default,,0,0,0,,BB Goat,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.00,0:06:12.00,Default,,0,0,0,,give the Super Cube to me, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.16,0:06:14.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I’ll help you return it to Mr. Slowy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.66,0:06:18.50,Default,,0,0,0,,If you play with me, I’ll give it to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.83,0:06:22.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, I’ll play with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.08,0:06:32.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I can’t take it anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.83,0:06:39.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Watch it for me. I’m catching a butterfly!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.00,0:06:41.50,Default,,0,0,0,,My hard work paid off!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.25,0:06:51.08,Default,,0,0,0,,How am I supposed to get gadgets, though?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.66,0:06:54.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I remember that when Weslie got his,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.16,0:06:56.16,Default,,0,0,0,,he held a very particular posture.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.66,0:06:57.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Perhaps…?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.25,0:07:02.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on out, my gadgets!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.91,0:07:06.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Was…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.66,0:07:08.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Was my posture not right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.91,0:07:11.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I’ll try a few more and see.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.75,0:07:14.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on out, my gadgets!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.50,0:07:18.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Come out! Come out!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.66,0:07:20.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing’s happening.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.83,0:07:25.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Slowy says to read a lot of books when running into problems.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.33,0:07:27.25,Default,,0,0,0,,The answer must be in here somewhere!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.08,0:07:31.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I don’t understand it at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.33,0:07:35.58,Default,,0,0,0,,It’s Paddi’s voice!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.41,0:07:42.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Paddi,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.00,0:07:44.41,Default,,0,0,0,,don’t worry! I’m coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.91,0:07:47.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.08,0:07:51.33,Default,,0,0,0,,do you really need to cry out so loudly when you fall?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.50,0:07:54.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Right, Weslie’s here, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.50,0:07:56.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess there’s nothing I can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.58,0:07:58.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I was picking apples,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.75,0:08:01.00,Default,,0,0,0,,but all of a sudden, ice formed right here,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.66,0:08:03.00,Default,,0,0,0,,and I slipped.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.33,0:08:04.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Ice?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.50,0:08:06.50,Default,,0,0,0,,How did a patch of ice form here?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.33,0:08:09.25,Default,,0,0,0,,That was me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.83,0:08:11.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Look out!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.91,0:08:15.91,Default,,0,0,0,,What… What the…?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.00,0:08:18.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Has Wolffy gotten possessed by bacteria again?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.00,0:08:23.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Hand over BB Goat right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.41,0:08:26.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Run! Run!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.58,0:08:30.08,Default,,0,0,0,,What a big refrigerator!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.16,0:08:35.66,Default,,0,0,0,,There you are!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.08,0:08:39.91,Default,,0,0,0,,BB Goat!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.91,0:08:46.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Take BB Goat and run.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.50,0:08:47.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I’ll slow him down.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.66,0:08:51.16,Default,,0,0,0,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.75,0:08:55.08,Default,,0,0,0,,There’s more!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.08,0:09:01.16,Default,,0,0,0,,What now?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.75,0:09:04.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Just give up already!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.58,0:09:06.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Hand over BB Goat!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.25,0:09:09.25,Default,,0,0,0,,You’ll have to get past me first!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.58,0:09:11.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Bring it on!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.33,0:09:19.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Where’d he go?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.33,0:09:22.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Now!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.83,0:09:26.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.00,0:09:33.83,Default,,0,0,0,,See how powerful I am now?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.83,0:09:35.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Weslie!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.58,0:09:37.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I’m fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.25,0:09:40.25,Default,,0,0,0,,It’s so cold!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.33,0:09:43.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Nope, I’m catching a cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.33,0:09:44.08,Default,,0,0,0,,He’s stalling!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.50,0:09:51.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I’m King Bacteria, you know!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.41,0:09:53.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You’ve been fooled once again!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.83,0:09:58.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Weslie!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.25,0:10:01.00,Default,,0,0,0,,So what if you’re fast?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.41,0:10:03.00,Default,,0,0,0,,It’s not like there’s nothing I can do about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.33,0:10:04.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Look out, guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.16,0:10:10.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Paddi!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.08,0:10:14.00,Default,,0,0,0,,It’s so icy and cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.50,0:10:18.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Worry about yourself first!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.75,0:10:27.66,Default,,0,0,0,,You have nowhere to run!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.33,0:10:34.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Sparky!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.91,0:10:44.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Brother Sparky!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.08,0:10:48.58,Default,,0,0,0,,No one can stop me now!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.25,0:10:51.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You’re coming with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.75,0:10:57.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Brother Sparky!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.50,0:11:00.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Why is it
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.41,0:11:04.33,Default,,0,0,0,,that I can only stand and watch when my friends are hurt?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.50,0:11:07.33,Default,,0,0,0,,If only I were more powerful.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.00,0:11:09.08,Default,,0,0,0,,If only I were stronger.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.83,0:11:14.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to protect my friends, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.16,0:11:23.00,Default,,0,0,0,,What’s happening?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.83,0:11:35.58,Default,,0,0,0,,What the…?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.75,0:11:38.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.08,0:11:46.50,Default,,0,0,0,,There’s more!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.08,0:11:55.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Are these my gadgets?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.16,0:11:57.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel warm all over.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.91,0:11:58.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Perhaps…?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.50,0:12:07.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.75,0:12:10.41,Default,,0,0,0,,It looks like my gadgets can control heat!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.25,0:12:13.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Let’s take him down together, Sparky!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.08,0:12:19.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Don’t get cocky just yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.33,0:12:29.83,Default,,0,0,0,,What a nuisance, jumping here and there!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.00,0:12:32.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Don’t forget about {\i1}me!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.50,0:12:40.25,Default,,0,0,0,,It’s so hot! I’m burning!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.25,0:12:41.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I hate heat!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.66,0:12:49.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I’ll be back!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.58,0:12:54.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Great job, Sparky!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.83,0:12:56.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Where am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.00,0:12:59.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel sore all over after that nap.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.50,0:13:02.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Wolffy, you were possessed by bacteria again.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.75,0:13:03.66,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.08,0:13:07.08,Default,,0,0,0,,If you were as hygienic as I am,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.66,0:13:09.25,Default,,0,0,0,,you’d stop getting possessed.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.08,0:13:17.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess the security system still needs some work.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.33,0:13:18.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Sparky?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.75,0:13:19.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.16,0:13:22.83,Default,,0,0,0,,You may also have gadgets now,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.00,0:13:25.50,Default,,0,0,0,,but with bigger powers come bigger responsibilities.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.75,0:13:27.50,Default,,0,0,0,,What are your thoughts on this?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.00,0:13:32.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I may have my own gadgets now,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.08,0:13:34.83,Default,,0,0,0,,but the most important thing
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.83,0:13:37.58,Default,,0,0,0,,is to have a desire to help others,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.83,0:13:40.41,Default,,0,0,0,,no matter how big or small your powers are.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.00,0:13:42.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.41,0:13:45.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Sparky, come help!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.91,0:13:49.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.50,0:13:50.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Heat water for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.75,0:13:51.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Heat my towel!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.41,0:13:54.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Heat my food!
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:05.00,Default,,0,0,0,,------------------------------------------------------
